                rend="underline">usually called Hyperoxy <del rend="strikethrough">
                  <unclear>xxxxx</unclear>
               </del> muriates</hi>
            <lb/>
by Sir H Davy. LLD. FRS. -<lb/>
            <rs xmlns:conf="https://www.lancaster.ac.uk/library/ns/digital-library/config/1.0"
