                type="chemical">
               <term xml:id="tag166">
          chlorine
          
        </term>
            </rs> It destroys<lb/>
moist vegetable blues without previously reddening them<lb/>
When it is heated to a temperature about that of boiling wa-<lb/>
ter it explodes more violently than <rs xmlns:conf="https://www.lancaster.ac.uk/library/ns/digital-library/config/1.0"
