                 rend="strikethrough">manner. I shall call this lantern which should always</del>
            <lb/>
            <del xmlns:conf="https://www.lancaster.ac.uk/library/ns/digital-library/config/1.0"
                 rend="strikethrough">burn with a flame rather feebler than a lamp exposed to</del>
            <lb/>
            <del xmlns:conf="https://www.lancaster.ac.uk/library/ns/digital-library/config/1.0"
                 rend="strikethrough">free air the <hi rend="underline">safe lantern</hi>
            </del>
            <lb/>
            <del xmlns:conf="https://www.lancaster.ac.uk/library/ns/digital-library/config/1.0"
                 rend="strikethrough">I have two other lanterns made which I shall</del>
            <lb/>
