Very early in my enquiries on the explosive powers of mixtures of<lb/>
air with fire damp <del xmlns:conf="https://www.lancaster.ac.uk/library/ns/digital-library/config/1.0"
                 rend="strikethrough">I found that when fire damp or the gas</del>
