                 rend="strikethrough">the explosion was never</del>
            <lb/>
            <del xmlns:conf="https://www.lancaster.ac.uk/library/ns/digital-library/config/1.0"
                 rend="strikethrough">communicated through the tubes provided there was a current of</del>
            <lb/>
