               <add>far</add> as <add>was compatible</add>
               <del rend="strikethrough">possible</del>
               <lb/>
               <add>with their inflammation</add> the top of the cylinder <del rend="strikethrough">continued</del>
               <lb/>
for some minutes <add>was</add> strongly red<lb/>
