The heat communicated by flame<lb/>
must depend upon its <del rend="strikethrough">
                  <unclear>xxxx</unclear>
               </del> mass<lb/>
this is shewn by the fact that<lb/>
               <del rend="strikethrough">in a</del>
               <add>the top of a</add> slender cylinder of wire<lb/>
