through is <add>found</add> very hot for it will<lb/>
convert paper into <rs xml:id="ttag571" ref="#chemical_140" type="chemical">
                  <term xml:id="tag571">
          charcoal
          
        </term>
               </rs>, &amp; it<lb/>
